}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== 727095-004 is the model info on the MAC / model label on the top side of the board. In full, for this particular card, it reads '''009027A9DAC6 29913 727095-00'''.
The '''Intel''' 82559 chip is marked with... :*The big '''Intel i''' logo on the left side :*'''GD82559''' :*'''L913IE92''' :*'''(M)(C)'98''' :*'''KOREA''' "PB 721502-005" (PB code [??]) and "MP 721503-005" (MP code [??]) is etched onto the bottom of the board (along with some '''KALEX''' text).
There is no '''[[Intel]]''' logo anywhere on the card, however, the card has the noted '''Albany''' / '''Wisconsin''' FCC ID.
